StructureDefinitionKind

Defines the type of structure that a definition is describing

This value set has an inline code system http://hl7.org/fhir/structure-definition-kind, which defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
datatype Data TypeA data type - either a primitive or complex structure that defines a set of data elements. These can be used throughout Resource and extension definitions
resource ResourceA resource defined by the FHIR specification
